trans-unit.source: The AddRequest class adds an entry to the directory.
trans-unit.target: Klassen AddRequest lägger till en post i katalogen.

trans-unit.source: The request may be added to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument> or it can be used as the parameter for <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Begäran kan läggas till <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument>eller användas som parameter för <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument>

trans-unit.source: The AddRequest constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn AddRequest skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The AddRequest constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest"></xref> class using the specified distinguished name and attributes.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn AddRequest skapar en instans av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av angivna unika namn och attribut.

trans-unit.source: The `distinguishedName` of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: Den `distinguishedName` nytt objekt i katalogen.

trans-unit.source: An array, of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute"></xref> objects, that contains the attributes for this object.
trans-unit.target: En matris av <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute"> </xref> objekt som innehåller attributen för det här objektet.

trans-unit.source: This parameter may be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den här parametern kan vara <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The AddRequest constructor creates an instance of the class using the specified distinguishedName and the object class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn AddRequest skapar en instans av den klassen med hjälp av den angivna distinguishedName och object-klassen.

trans-unit.source: The value specified in the `objectClass` parameter is added to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Värdet som anges i den `objectClass` parameter läggs till i <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: This value can be modified after this constructor is called.
trans-unit.target: Det här värdet kan ändras när den här konstruktorn kallas.

trans-unit.source: The `distinguishedName` of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: Den `distinguishedName` nytt objekt i katalogen.

trans-unit.source: The object class for this object.
trans-unit.target: Object-klassen för det här objektet.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Om den här parametern <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>, genereras ett undantag.

trans-unit.source: The objectClass parameter contains a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Den objectClass parametern innehåller en null-referens ( i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The Attributes property contains a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection"></xref> of attribute-value pairs for the object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen attribut innehåller en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection"> </xref> för attribut-värde-par för objektet.

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen kan inte anges.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection"></xref> of attribute-value pairs for the object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection"> </xref> för attribut-värde-par för objektet.

trans-unit.source: The DistinguishedName property contains the distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen DistinguishedName innehåller det unika namnet för objektet.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: Det unika namnet för objektet.

trans-unit.source: The ToXmlNode method creates an XML node from the specified <xref href="System.Xml.XmlDocument"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ToXmlNode skapar en XML-nod från det angivna <xref href="System.Xml.XmlDocument"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Xml.XmlDocument"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Xml.XmlDocument"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: The resulting <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Det resulterande <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"> </xref> objekt.
